 the area of\nMontreal: the count of accidents on the same road segment during previous\nyears, the temperature, the day of the year, the hour and the visibility.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 May 2019 17:41:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Oct 2019 17:05:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 11 Nov 2019 18:50:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-02"}
