gree well. We conclude that the method verifies tension to\napproximately 2% (1 sigma) in a little over 1s for 1.5m wires, and would be\nfaster for shorter wires.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 May 2019 22:07:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-23"}
