 to\nthe Knaster--Tarski Fixed Point Theorem for lattices and theorems analogous to\nthe Tychonoff Theorem for topological spaces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 May 2019 09:23:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 28 Nov 2020 10:22:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-01"}
